data.description: Located in the sought-after Highland Woods neighborhood, this Ranch style cutie is waiting for its new owner. The open floorplan welcomes you the minute you enter the front door. Updated kitchen, bathrooms, waterproof vinyl throughout the house, recently painted exterior also new furnace & water heater. The large backyard is a perfect playground for kids & pets. The redwood deck offers a cozy outdoor experience. The owners have converted the garage to make a third bedroom (all permitted) the garage is only for storage at this point. It could be removed if the buyer desired or another option would be to extend the garage. The Tuff Shed has electricity, laminate flooring & would make an ideal office/hobby room or workshop. The central location offers easy access to bike paths, walking trails shopping & restaurants. Time to make it yours!
